    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"110049\">Mario Carneiro</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/287929-mathlib4/topic/Set.20theory.20without.20choice/near/463633936\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>With definite description, you can define quotients using sets in the usual ZF style</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yes. And you can also prove <code>Quot r</code> is the same as ZF style quotient.</p>",
